high_descs: Walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the egg from inside the sink.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the counter.
Put the egg inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the heated egg inside the fridge on the top shelf and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step to your left.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and take a step then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the egg in the fridge on the shelf above the tomato in the middle of the shelf near the from edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the fridge.

high_descs: Grab the egg out of the sink
Heat the egg in the microwave
Grab the egg back and walk over to the fridge
Place the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg and put it in the fridge
